               meson,
               sassc,
Standards-Version: 4.1.1
Homepage: https://github.com/ubuntu/gnome-shell-communitheme

Package: gnome-shell-theme-communitheme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: GNOME Shell Ubuntu Community Theme
 This is the theme that is shaped by the community on the Ubuntu hub.
 .
 This package contains the GNOME Shell theme part
 .
 More information if you want to follow the development on
 https://community.ubuntu.com/c/desktop/theme-refresh.

